&lt;p&gt;I like to keep a card view of my week within sight, but I find myself primarily alternating between this ‚ÄúCurrent Week‚Äù card view, and the all-encompassing ‚ÄúCalendar View‚Äù, allowing me to look at all events ahead on a clear calendar.&lt;/p&gt;
