&lt;p&gt;A prime example of a relational database I derive from this &lt;strong&gt;Master Schedule&lt;/strong&gt; is the view I link to within my &lt;strong&gt;The Great Outdoors&lt;/strong&gt; page, which is filtered using a defined &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;Category&lt;/code&gt; of ‚ÄúHiking‚Äù:&lt;/p&gt;
