&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Phoenix, AZ&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Attended &lt;a href=&quot;https://devmountain.com/phoenix-bootcamp&quot;&gt;DevMountain&lt;/a&gt;‚Äôs first iteration of its full-time web development program in Phoenix, Arizona. During Kylie‚Äôs time at this bootcamp, she was &lt;a href=&quot;https://downtowndevil.com/2017/09/05/86663/devmountain-coding-boot-camp/&quot;&gt;interviewed by a local periodical&lt;/a&gt; about her experience at DevMountain, collaborated with various teams to build a variety of projects, including a news distributor that took machine learning into account when dispensing article recommendations to its subscribers, and spoke at a &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.meetup.com/tr-TR/Phoenix-ReactJS/events/244438999/&quot;&gt;local meetup&lt;/a&gt; about her experience learning and implementing React Native.&lt;/p&gt;
